Package: countyhealthR
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic Access to County Health Rankings & Roadmaps Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hannah", "Olson-Williams", 
           email = "hannaheow@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Hannah Olson-Williams <hannaheow@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a simple interface to pull County Health Rankings & Roadmaps
  (CHR&R) county-level health data and metadata directly from Zenodo. Users can retrieve
  data for CHR&R release years 2010 through 2025. The
  package enables programmatic access similar to tidycensus.
